	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have several issues with my DS Lite. First, the L and R buttons barely work (if at all). They trigger when I don't want them to, and they don't trigger when I want them to. Second, the touch screen has a dent in it which throws it off. Third, the power switch broke, so I have to turn it on with a screwdriver. Is there any way I can fix any of these problems?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


